            <div type="apparatus">
               <p>Pending</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>Hail, Mary, full of grace. The Lord is with you.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Poor condition. Exfoliated. A cross with dots in the angles marks the beginning of the text. The word κεχαριτωμένη is misspelled. The inscription is based on the dialoque between the Archangel Gabriel and the Virgin according to Luke 1:28, 38. The addition of the name of the Virgin after Χαῖρε κεχαριτωμένη, which is absent in the evangelical text, appears also in the inscription of Sotera. </p>
            </div>
